{"tid":1804861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵本地線十一月份客量比去年同期下跌超過 24%","createTime":"2019-12-31T09:57:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T09:59:01.000Z","uid":213167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"afecbca8ba09bbe76369b8b39e3ff1cd1e71a78a","tid":1804861,"uid":213167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:57:19.000Z","msg":"港鐵本地線十一月份客量比上月微升，但比去年同期下跌超過 24%，其他如過境路線均有下跌趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵本地服務總客量：110,311,000 人次<br />\n<br />\n比十月份上升 1,855,000 人次 (1.71%)，比去年同期下跌 35,436,000 人次 (24.31%)<br />\n機場快綫亦有相同趨勢<br />\n<br />\n過境綫 (羅湖/落馬洲)、城際客運、輕鐵、港鐵巴士及高速鐵路的客量比十月份和去年同期均下跌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef: <a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcorporate%2Finvestor%2Fpatronage.php%23search&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJlUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=68db1fc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search</a><br />\n<br />\n做法不完美，但可接受，要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e70288ed1d96734cc0e8181e4124340ad6c1a0","tid":1804861,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:58:56.000Z","msg":"同我跌夠50%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2d6698fee1de0d670a437ebdec5a19c4f16b23","tid":1804861,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"德美 聯署 整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"}]}